 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>

2014年，他上传了[[印度政府|印度政府]]保密50年之久的《[[亨德森·布鲁克斯报告|亨德森·布鲁克斯报告]]》到互联网上。<ref name="unnithan">{{cite news |last=Unnithan |first=Sandeep |title=Henderson Brooks report lists the guilty men of 1962 |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/the-guilty-men-of-1962-india-china-war-jawahar-lal-nehru-krishna-menon/1/350080.html |accessdate=8 April 2014 |newspaper=India Today |date=18 March 2014 |archive-date=2018-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103084116/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/the-guilty-men-of-1962-india-china-war-jawahar-lal-nehru-krishna-menon/1/350080.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 这份报告1962年由印度军方撰写，主要分析了中印边境战争中印度失利的原因。<ref name="pandalai">{{cite news |last=Pandalai |first=Shruti |title=Burying Open Secrets: India's 1962 War and the Henderson-Brooks Report |url=http://southasia.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2014/04/02/burying_open_secrets_indias_1962_war_and_the_henderson_brooks_report |accessdate=8 April 2014 |newspaper=Foreign Policy |date=2 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408224604/http://southasia.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2014/04/02/burying_open_secrets_indias_1962_war_and_the_henderson_brooks_report |archivedate=2014年4月8日 }}</ref>但印度境内无法阅读该报告。印度当局也拒绝解释原因。<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2014/03/140318_india_china_war_report 印度拒絕解密1962年中印戰爭報告] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2014/03/140318_india_china_war_report |date=20200911010439 }}，BBC中文网。</ref>

